metadata.name: Royal Dog I
metadata.description:
Royal Dog I. Neapolitan Mastiff.

If I could place a crown upon the head of every dog in the world, I would.

Their undying loyalty to their family is to be admired. 

My career in creating art with dogs began in 2003. The ‘Royal Dog’ portraits serve as a way to honor these incredible animals – both for their regal stature and the loyalty that is so deeply ingrained inside of them.
